Joint demo
==========

SDR
---
/root/d.sh

./sdr-ad-hoc-join.sh sdr0 11 192.168.13.20 2A:E1:77:xx:xx:xx

# ping Wi-Fi dongle
ping 192.168.13.15 -i 0.1

# Add default routing for eth0 to send back (to sdr_orch) packets outside our subnet (10.2.0.0/16)
ip route add default dev eth0

# Start imec controller after gateway is added to monster laptop
cd /root/y2sc3/controllers
./imec_controller.py


Laptop
------
./sdr-ad-hoc-up.sh wlx00c0ca84636a 11 192.168.13.15

# Put SDR as defualt gateway to laptop
sudo route add -net 10.2.0.0 netmask 255.255.0.0 gw 192.168.13.20 dev wlx00c0ca84636a
sudo route add -net 10.0.0.0 netmask 255.255.0.0 gw 192.168.13.20 dev wlx00c0ca84636a
sudo route add -net 10.97.0.0 netmask 255.255.0.0 gw 192.168.13.20 dev wlx00c0ca84636a

Solo demo
=========

dongle
------
Wait dongle Wi-Fi to get started and retreive the ad-hoc slice ID


SDR
---
./sdr-ad-hoc-join.sh sdr0 11 192.168.13.20 02:11:87:xx:xx:xx
./sdr-ad-hoc-join.sh sdr0 11 192.168.13.20 xx:xx:xx:xx:xx:xx

# ping Wi-Fi dongle
ping 192.168.13.13 -i 0.1

# Ping iphone
ping 192.168.13.25 -i 0.1

# Change Wi-FI dongle to low latency mode
iw/iw dev sdr0 set addr0 4cf855aa
iw/iw dev sdr0 set addr0 ca84636a

# Change iphone to low duty cycle mode
iw/iw dev sdr0 set addr1 33044abf


Laptop
------

connect to ORCA network

# After ping test, start vlc demo
nice -n 1 vlc udp://@:1234



